      871,
      1068,
      928
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Vì $CC' // (AA'BB') \\Rightarrow d(CC'; AB') = d(C; (AA'BB')) = CH = \\sqrt{3} \\approx 1,73$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
